# Security Policy

## Supported Versions

| Version | Supported          |
| ------- | ------------------ |
| 5.1.x   | :white_check_mark: |
| 5.0.x   | :x:                |
| 4.0.x   | :white_check_mark: |
| < 4.0   | :x:                |

## Reporting a Vulnerability

If you find any vulnerabilites, please report them in the [issues page](https://github.com/Ascendus/RN-Discord-Bot/issues).
